                        Flavor: Very sweet, with low acidity.
                        Flesh: Greenish-white, firm, crispy, and juicy.
                        Origin: Italy.
                        Tree: Moderate growth, with a typical spur character.
                        Blooms: Mid-early, a few days before Golden Delicious.
                        Pollinators: Granny Smith, Golden Delicious, Idared, Gala, Fuji.
                        Yield: High and uniform.
                        Maturation: Mid-September.</p>
